{"id":172940,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/08/朝圣！《red-star-2-0》体验手记-传说中的朝鲜操作系统～-imobi/","date":"2011-08-18T16:00:04Z","modified":"2011-08-18T16:00:04Z","title":"朝圣！《Red Star 2.0》体验手记 传说中的朝鲜操作系统～- iMobile365","content":"<div>\n<h1>朝圣！《Red Star 2.0》体验手记</h1>\n<p><span><a href=\"http://imobile365.com/author/plum\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/d32c5e3fd02cc448ceecab5e2f859b33?s=35&#038;d=http%3A%2F%2F1.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D35&#038;r=G\" height=\"35\" width=\"35\" /></a></span></div>\n<div>\n<p>很久很久以前，我得知在我国的临邦，有一个名叫朝鲜的美好国度，他们的计算机产业异常发达，已经研发出了属于自己的操作系统，那就是红星2.0(Red Star 2.0)，我对于这么一个神奇的系统一直心怀向往，那么在近日，它的ISO镜像终于在海盗湾上泄漏出来了，于是乎我便迫不及待的开始下载并安装了起来。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_039.png\" rel=\"fancybox\"><img title=\"选区_039\" src=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_039-500x394.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"394\" /></a></p>\n<p><span></span></p>\n<h3><strong>Installion</strong></h3>\n<p>对于这么一个系统，贸然的刻盘安装是最大的不敬，所以我选择了用Vbox先行。系统支持光盘启动，首先映入眼帘的是强大的安装介绍，虽然我看不懂，但是感觉很霸气的样子。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://imobile365.com/articles/5279/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_019\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-5280\"><img title=\"选区_019\" src=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_019-500x397.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"397\" /></a></p>\n<p>接下来就是安装分区选择，红星系统只支持EXT3 Swap 和Vfat，想来也是，支持那么多有个鸟用，常用的还不就是这几个，不过安装系统居然不能自动分区，也罢，朝鲜人民是辛劳智慧的，分区还是手动分好点。</p>\n<div><a href=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_020.png\" rel=\"fancybox\"><img title=\"选区_020\" src=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_020-500x396.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"396\" /></a></p>\n<p>分区</p>\n</div>\n<div><a href=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_021.png\" rel=\"fancybox\"><img title=\"选区_021\" src=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_021-500x395.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"395\" /></a></p>\n<p>只支持这三个格式</p>\n</div>\n<div><a href=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_022.png\" rel=\"fancybox\"><img title=\"选区_022\" src=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_022-500x392.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"392\" /></a></p>\n<p>ext3 / vfat / swap</p>\n</div>\n<div><a href=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_023.png\" rel=\"fancybox\"><img title=\"选区_023\" src=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_023-500x395.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"395\" /></a></p>\n<p>分区完毕</p>\n</div>\n<div><a href=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_024.png\" rel=\"fancybox\"><img title=\"选区_024\" src=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_024-500x396.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"396\" /></a></p>\n<p>写入MBR</p>\n</div>\n<p>然后就是网卡设置</p>\n<div><a href=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_025.png\" rel=\"fancybox\"><img title=\"选区_025\" src=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_025-500x399.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"399\" /></a></p>\n<p>网卡设置</p>\n</div>\n<p>接着是管理员设置</p>\n<div><a href=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_026.png\" rel=\"fancybox\"><img title=\"选区_026\" src=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_026-500x393.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"393\" /></a></p>\n<p>管理员设置</p>\n</div>\n<p>然后……没有然后了，开始安装了。</p>\n<div><a href=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_027.png\" rel=\"fancybox\"><img title=\"选区_027\" src=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_027-500x395.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"395\" /></a></p>\n<p>安装中</p>\n</div>\n<p>我是i5 750的机器，给虚拟机分配了512MB内存，安装了大约快半个小时……我知道红星2.0一定是采用现场编译安装的，所以才会这么慢。</p>\n<h3><strong>Booting</strong></h3>\n<p>安装完毕后我们就可以启动系统了，第一次进入系统，我们看到了鼠标周围的蓝色光圈，似曾相识，对了，一定是Fedora Core 5抄袭的红星2.0妥妥儿的。</p>\n<div><a href=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_028.png\" rel=\"fancybox\"><img title=\"选区_028\" src=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_028.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"279\" /></a></p>\n<p>似曾相识的鼠标标示</p>\n</div>\n<p>一个伟大的仙鹤配合一个大大的ROOT字样的登录界面出现了，没有丝毫拖泥带水的感觉。对于普通用户来说直接用ROOT完全没啥问题，设置一个新管理员账户神马的都是脱了裤子放屁多此一举。</p>\n<div><a href=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_029.png\" rel=\"fancybox\"><img title=\"选区_029\" src=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_029-500x395.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"395\" /></a></p>\n<p>Login</p>\n</div>\n<p>进入界面立即就震撼了，标准的UI，清爽而又简洁，采用了最新的KDE技术，世界顶尖水平。无论是图标还是界面都是独立设计，才没有抄袭Windows XP神马的呢！</p>\n<div><a href=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_030.png\" rel=\"fancybox\"><img title=\"选区_030\" src=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_030-500x373.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"373\" /></a></p>\n<p>KDE，还内置了中文字体哦</p>\n</div>\n<h3><strong>Hacking</strong></h3>\n<p>翻来翻去，我找不到”终端”，我知道这一定是组织在考验我。</p>\n<div><a href=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_032.png\" rel=\"fancybox\"><img title=\"选区_032\" src=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_032-500x394.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"394\" /></a></p>\n<p>控制面板里要啥有啥，就是没有终端</p>\n</div>\n<p>最后我终于在/usr/bin/下手动启动了konsole终端……内牛满面。</p>\n<div><a href=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_034.png\" rel=\"fancybox\"><img title=\"选区_034\" src=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_034-500x395.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"395\" /></a></p>\n<p>终端！</p>\n</div>\n<p>我原本以为这将会是2.4内核，看来是我觉悟太低了，居然是2.6内核的。</p>\n<div><a href=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_040.png\" rel=\"fancybox\"><img title=\"选区_040\" src=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_040-500x379.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"379\" /></a></p>\n<p>2.6内核</p>\n</div>\n<p>红星2.0内置的浏览器是独立开发的思密达2.0浏览器。</p>\n<div><a href=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_031.png\" rel=\"fancybox\"><img title=\"选区_031\" src=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_031-500x395.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"395\" /></a></p>\n<p>思密达2.0浏览器</p>\n</div>\n<p>思密达2.0浏览器的搜索引擎只有俩，我尝试添加Google……然后……挂掉了，啊不对，是失去响应了，还有人性化窗口提示关闭未响应程序。请无视那个firefox-bin，那是迷惑人用的。</p>\n<div><a href=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_037.png\" rel=\"fancybox\"><img title=\"选区_037\" src=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_037-500x396.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"396\" /></a></p>\n<p>firefox-bin</p>\n</div>\n<p>我还在/usr/bin/中找到了KDE默认的浏览器Konqueror，然后浏览了以下网页就报错了，看来美帝的玩意就是不可靠，难怪这玩意被从菜单里删掉了。</p>\n<div><a href=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_041.png\" rel=\"fancybox\"><img title=\"选区_041\" src=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_041-500x393.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"393\" /></a></p>\n<p>konqueror</p>\n</div>\n<div><a href=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_042.png\" rel=\"fancybox\"><img title=\"选区_042\" src=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_042-500x280.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"280\" /></a></p>\n<p>崩溃的总是很快</p>\n</div>\n<p>红星2.0作为这么一个优秀的系统，我更希望它能显示中文，于是我开始进行KDE的设置，Kconfig……</p>\n<div><a href=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_043.png\" rel=\"fancybox\"><img title=\"选区_043\" src=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_043-500x387.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"387\" /></a></p>\n<p>控制面板</p>\n</div>\n<p>结果是这么一个控制面板……里面啥都有，就是没有系统语言。</p>\n<p>我不死心，想要强行修改locale，不过找遍了系统各个角落，没有任何关于locale的设置信息，常用的配置文件都不好使。</p>\n<p>最后强行替换ko_KP为zh_CN，重启后思密达依旧……</p>\n<p>好吧，我的小把戏太过天真了。</p>\n<h3><strong>Software</strong></h3>\n<p>既然修改不成，那么看看yum功能吧，在Konsole中输入yum update。</p>\n<div><a href=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_044.png\" rel=\"fancybox\"><img title=\"选区_044\" src=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_044-500x376.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"376\" /></a></p>\n<p>Yum</p>\n</div>\n<p>失败了……而且有趣的是，红星2.0拥有自己的软件源管理器，但是完全不可用……</p>\n<p>我突然想起来下载的时候还有一张软件安装盘，加载进去看看。</p>\n<p>果然是传说中的软件大礼包，安装起来如何呢？</p>\n<div><a href=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_038.png\" rel=\"fancybox\"><img title=\"选区_038\" src=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_038-500x389.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"389\" /></a></p>\n<p>软件</p>\n</div>\n<p>和Windows一样人性化！双击安装向导！红星2.0就是无敌！另外，安装软件必须要求你是Root哦。</p>\n<div><a href=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_035.png\" rel=\"fancybox\"><img title=\"选区_035\" src=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_035-500x393.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"393\" /></a></p>\n<p>Root</p>\n</div>\n<p>装了一个Office类的软件，我这时才注意到右下角的scim输入法，还可以输入中文。</p>\n<div><a href=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_046.png\" rel=\"fancybox\"><img title=\"选区_046\" src=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_046-500x397.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"397\" /></a></p>\n<p>中文输入</p>\n</div>\n<h3><strong>End</strong></h3>\n<p>经过了一系列体验后，我深深的感受到了红星2.0系统在各方面的优越性和博大精深……来日方长，看来我还得慢慢钻研才行啊。</p>\n<p>如果你想要种子的话，可以<a href=\"http://imobile365.com/achieve/RedStar.rar\">点击这里</a>，下载。</p>\n<div><a href=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_036.png\" rel=\"fancybox\"><img title=\"选区_036\" src=\"http://imobile365.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/%E9%80%89%E5%8C%BA_036-500x402.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"402\" /></a></p>\n<p>Grub启动</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[20534],"tags":[]}